{
  "stem": "24409.3",
  "chunk_idx": 5,
  "model": "openai/gpt-oss-120b",
  "elapsed_s": 11.3,
  "sentences_input": [
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 15,
      "text": "And there was all kinds of windows high up in the room, in the basement.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 16,
      "text": "It was a school basement.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 17,
      "text": "And we wrote notes, several of us, and I wrote two notes, one to my brother, and one to [?",
      "word_count": 20
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 18,
      "text": "Eric ?] [?",
      "word_count": 3
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 19,
      "text": "Wolfe, ?] in which I said, continue with the action.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 11,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 20,
      "text": "My arrest has nothing to do with the action.",
      "word_count": 9
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And how do you deliver this?",
      "word_count": 6
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "You saw people walking by, and you saw a guard marching by slowly.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 12,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "So we figured how long it takes the guard to go to the corner and come back, for the time shortly after he marched in one direction was the time when we could send a paper out if somebody came.",
      "word_count": 40
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And a woman came shortly after the guards had gone in one direction.",
      "word_count": 13
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "And I throw up a little ball of paper to her sitting up on the back of somebody else.",
      "word_count": 19
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "Which I said, [NON-ENGLISH], I said so she should stop.",
      "word_count": 10
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 3,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 4,
      "text": "So she stopped and then I threw this paper out and other people threw papers out, too.",
      "word_count": 17
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 5,
      "text": "And she picks them up, and the guard came back again, after he had [INAUDIBLE].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 6,
      "text": "And now I knew that she had done some thinking about it.",
      "word_count": 12
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 7,
      "text": "Now [PAUSES FOR 6 SECONDS] the nice thing was that I heard my name called.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 8,
      "text": "[NON-ENGLISH], [NON-ENGLISH], means Jew who is in protective custody, Perl, it was my title [NON-ENGLISH].",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 9,
      "text": "So I went to see what it is.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 10,
      "text": "This must already have to do with these pieces of paper.",
      "word_count": 11
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 11,
      "text": "And there was a Viennese police officer there.",
      "word_count": 8
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 12,
      "text": "I forgot his name now.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 13,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 13,
      "text": "But it's in my book.",
      "word_count": 5
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 0,
      "text": "And he asked me, we have here a man, he says, do you know Mr.",
      "word_count": 15
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 1,
      "text": "Diamand?",
      "word_count": 1
    },
    {
      "segment_idx": 14,
      "sentence_idx_in_seg": 2,
      "text": "I said, I know several Diamands.",
      "word_count": 6
    }
  ],
